#. Main menu item
#: ../nobootloader.templates:4
msgid "Continue without boot loader"
msgstr "Mynd ymlaen heb lwythydd bŵt"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Some variables need to be set in the Genesi firmware in order for your "
"system to boot automatically.  At the end of the installation, the system "
"will reboot.  At the firmware prompt, set the following firmware variables "
"to enable auto-booting:"
msgstr ""
"Rhaid gosod rhai newidynnau yn y OpenFirmware Pegasos er mwyn i'ch system "
"fŵtio Debian yn awtomatig. Ar ddiwedd y sefydliad, fe fydd y system yn "
"ailfŵtio. Ger y hybydd OpenFirmware Pegasos, gosodwch y newidynnau "
"OpenFirmware canlynol er mwyn galluogi bŵtio awtomatig:"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you will be able to boot the kernel manually by entering, at "
"the firmware prompt:"
msgstr "Neu fe allwch fŵtio'r cnewyllyn â llaw gan roi :"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:31
msgid "Setting firmware variables for automatic boot"
msgstr "Gosod newidynnau cadarnwedd ar gyfer bŵt awtomatig"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:31
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Some variables need to be set in the Netwinder NeTTrom firmware in order for "
"your system to boot linux automatically.  At the end of this installation "
"stage, the system will reboot, and the firmware will attempt to autoboot.  "
"You can abort this by pressing any key. You will then be dropped into the "
"NeTTrom command system where you have to execute the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"Rhaid gosod rhai newidynnau yn y cadarnwedd NeTTrom Netwinder er mwyn i'ch "
"system fŵtio Debian yn awtomatig. Ar ddiwedd cam yma'r sefydliad, fe fydd y "
"system yn ailfŵtio, a bydd y cadarnwedd yn ceisio bŵtio'n awtomatig. Gallwch "
"rwystro hyn gan wasgu unrhyw fysell. Fe gewch yna eich rhoi yn y system "
"gorchmynion NeTTrom lle mae'n rhaid i chi weithredu'r gorchmynion canlynol:"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:31
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You will only need to do this once.  Afterwards, enter the \"boot\" command "
"or reboot the system to proceed to your newly installed system."
msgstr ""
"Fe fydd rhaid i chi wneud hyn unwaith yn unig. Ar ôl hynny, defnyddiwch y "
"gorchymyn \"boot\" neu ailfŵtiwch y system er mwyn mynd ymlaen at gam nesaf "
"sefydlu Debian."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:51
msgid "No boot loader installed"
msgstr "Dim llwythydd bŵt wedi ei sefydlu"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:51
msgid ""
"No boot loader has been installed, either because you chose not to or "
"because your specific architecture doesn't support a boot loader yet."
msgstr ""
"Does dim llwythydd bŵt wedi cael ei sefydlu, un ai oherwydd dewisoch chi "
"beidio, neu oherwydd dyw eich pensaerniaeth penodol ddim yn cynnal llwythydd "
"bŵt eto."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../nobootloader.templates:51
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You will need to boot manually with the ${KERNEL} kernel on partition "
"${BOOT} and ${ROOT} passed as a kernel argument."
msgstr ""
"Bydd rhaid i chi fŵtio â llaw gyda'r cnewyllyn ${KERNEL} ar y rhaniad "
"${BOOT} a gyda ${ROOT} wedi ei benodi fel ymresymiad cnewyllyn."
